    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Mesh convergence (GCI 1.4%), turbulence model validation against PIV data, and hemolysis index agreement within ±15% collectively support the claim that the CFD model reliably identifies worst-case hemolysis conditions. Six factors appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40 Table 3 for MRL 2 with medium model influence and high decision consequence. The UoA is accepted for regulatory submission supporting the Class II CPB device tolerance analysis.",
